<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.3">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://chu-jiaming.github.io//feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://chu-jiaming.github.io//" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="en"/><updated>2024-08-25T10:01:27+00:00</updated><id>https://chu-jiaming.github.io//feed.xml</id><title type="html">blank</title><subtitle>A simple, whitespace theme for academics. Based on [*folio](https://github.com/bogoli/-folio) design. </subtitle><entry><title type="html">Shell 学习笔记</title><link href="https://chu-jiaming.github.io//blog/2024/Shell/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Shell 学习笔记"/><published>2024-08-25T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2024-08-25T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://chu-jiaming.github.io//blog/2024/Shell</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://chu-jiaming.github.io//blog/2024/Shell/"><![CDATA[<h2 id="头部注释">头部注释</h2> <p>表明脚本文件所使用的解释器。</p> <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">#!/bin/bash</span>
</code></pre></div></div> <h2 id="基本命令">基本命令</h2> <h3 id="文件和目录操作">文件和目录操作</h3> <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">pwd</span>     <span class="c">#显示当前目录</span>
<span class="nb">ls</span>      <span class="c">#显示当前目录下的文件</span>
<span class="nb">cd</span>      <span class="c">#切换目录</span>
<span class="nb">mkdir</span>   <span class="c">#创建目录</span>
<span class="nb">touch</span>   <span class="c">#创建文件</span>
<span class="nb">rm</span>      <span class="c">#删除文件</span>
<span class="nb">rmdir</span>   <span class="c">#删除目录</span>
<span class="nb">cp</span>      <span class="c">#复制文件</span>
<span class="nb">mv</span>      <span class="c">#移动文件</span>
</code></pre></div></div> <h3 id="文件内容操作">文件内容操作</h3> <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">cat</span>     <span class="c">#查看文件内容</span>
</code></pre></div></div> <h3 id="文件权限操作">文件权限操作</h3> <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">chmod</span>   <span class="c">#修改文件权限</span>
<span class="nb">chown</span>   <span class="c">#修改文件所有者</span>
<span class="nb">chgrp</span>   <span class="c">#修改文件所属组</span>
</code></pre></div></div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="StudyNotes"/><category term="Shell"/><category term="Linux"/><category term="正则表达式"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Shell Study Notes]]></summary></entry></feed>